    类和说明
    Bean
    The Bean Class is entity class that mapping to a table,
    work with Helper, you can load/update/delete data from DB(RDS/Mongo), almost includes all methods that need for database
  • org.giiwa.bean使用的org.giiwa.dao中的类 
    类和说明
    Bean
    The Bean Class is entity class that mapping to a table,
    work with Helper, you can load/update/delete data from DB(RDS/Mongo), almost includes all methods that need for database
    BeanDAO
    the DAO helper class, used to access database
    Beans
    The Beans Class used to contains the Bean in query.
    Column
    the Column Class used to annotate the Bean, define the collection/table mapping with the Bean
    Helper.V
    Values in SQL, used to insert or update data both RDS and Mongo
    .
    Helper.W
    the W Class used to create SQL "where" conditions
    this is for RDS and Mongo Query.
    Table
    the Mapping Class used to annotate the Bean, define the collection/table mapping with the Bean name, the table name

    Values in SQL, used to insert or update data both RDS and Mongo
    .
    Helper.W
    the W Class used to create SQL "where" conditions
    this is for RDS and Mongo Query.
    Helper.W.Entity
    get all the condition elements
    Helper.W.OP 
    IAccess 
    MongoHelper
    The MongoHelper Class is base class for all class that database access, it almost includes all methods that need for database
    all data access MUST be inherited from it
    RDSHelper
    The RDSHelper Class is base class for all class that database access, it almost includes all methods that need for database
    all data access MUST be inherited from it
    TimeStamp
    The TimeStamp Class used to create a time stamp

    The X Class used to define contains.
